        public static WarcRecord readNextWarcRecord(LineAndChunkReader warcInLineReader,
                            boolean readContent)
                                     throws IOException
        Reads wbRecordReader a WARC record from a data input stream
        Parameters:
        warcInLineReader - line reader for the stream.
        readContent - indicate whether the content of the record is needed, as opposed to just the WARC header info.
        Returns:
        a WARC record (or null if eof)
